- `GET /api/vault/persona-memory/mimic/:id/performance` ƒ?" Retrieve persona's session/task analytics and performance history
- `POST /api/vault/persona-memory/mimic/:id/fork` ƒ?" Fork or duplicate persona for a new purpose
- `POST /api/vault/persona-memory/mimic/:id/merge` ƒ?" Merge two personas or archives
- `POST /api/vault/persona-memory/mimic/:id/archive` ƒ?" Archive persona or session
- `GET /api/vault/persona-memory/mimic/:id/export` ƒ?" Export all data for review/audit
- `POST /api/vault/persona-memory/mimic/import` ƒ?" Import persona memory (schema- and version-aware)
- `GET /api/vault/persona-memory/mimic/:id/audit` ƒ?" Full audit log for any persona's lifecycle and memory changes

**All endpoints enforce role/attribute permissions and are fully auditable.**

